\newlabel{tab:control}{{4}{25}{Discriminating controls for the locking metric (Pos\,3, $Re_P=100$, layers L13-L17, evaluated on a common grid). Within-topology values reproduce Fig.~\ref {fig:Ln}; cross-topology values are much lower, confirming that the de-rotation does not manufacture similarity.\relax }{table.caption.15}{}}
