\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {14}{\ignorespaces Topology contrast of the mean flow organisation at Pos\,3, $Re_P = 100$ (experiment left, simulation right in each panel): (a)\nobreakspace  {}the $30^\circ $ packing forms coherent, near-parallel slit jets with orderly recirculation; (b)\nobreakspace  {}the $40^\circ $ packing shows more inclined jets and stronger cross-flow swirl; (c)\nobreakspace  {}the irregular packing produces a single dominant channel with scattered, disorganised vortices and no banded structure. The progression from organised to erratic transport mirrors the locking parameter, which is near unity for the regular packings and collapses for the irregular one.\relax }}{30}{figure.caption.18}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:topocontrast}{{14}{30}{Topology contrast of the mean flow organisation at Pos\,3, $Re_P = 100$ (experiment left, simulation right in each panel): (a)~the $30^\circ $ packing forms coherent, near-parallel slit jets with orderly recirculation; (b)~the $40^\circ $ packing shows more inclined jets and stronger cross-flow swirl; (c)~the irregular packing produces a single dominant channel with scattered, disorganised vortices and no banded structure. The progression from organised to erratic transport mirrors the locking parameter, which is near unity for the regular packings and collapses for the irregular one.\relax }{figure.caption.18}{}}
